Tu te souviens ?

744
01:13:43,730 --> 01:13:46,320
Ton petit accident de laboratoire ?

745
01:13:47,940 --> 01:13:49,950
La stimulation des performances ?

746
01:13:51,360 --> 01:13:52,570
Moi.

747
01:13:52,910 --> 01:13:55,160
Ta plus grande création.

748
01:13:55,740 --> 01:13:59,290
